RIKER, Respondent, v. DUN et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, First, Department. February 16, 1894.) Action by Carroll L. Riker against Robert G. Dun and others..

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and O’BRIEN and FOLLETT, JJ.

J. B. Mullaly, for appellants. W. Parker, for respondent.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
